80. Build a test cookie with the setcookie( ) function using PHP.
code:
<?php
// Syntax: setcookie(name, value, expire, path, domain, secure, httponly);

// Create a test cookie valid for 1 hour
setcookie("TestCookie", "HelloCookie", time() + 3600, "/");

if (isset($_COOKIE["TestCookie"])) {
    echo "âœ… Cookie Value: " . $_COOKIE["TestCookie"];
} else {
    echo "ðŸª TestCookie has been set. Please refresh the page to read it.";
}
?>
